With extensive experience designing for a vast array of industries, working for both advertising agency and company, I am passionate about the creation, maintenance and development of brands.
I am capable of seeing a creative projects from concept through to production. I consider myself to be a problem-solver when it comes to creative direction and execution, plus I have a heightened attention to detail as a creative artworker.
I like to be surrounded by truly inspiring people, who are passionate about what they do, who are hungry to achieve more and who can help me grow in ways I couldn’t imagine.

I'm french living in Bologna. Since I always been in love with Italy after a 3 years working experience in Geneva I chose to move in Italy and settled in Milan for one years where I passed a Master’s Degree in Art Direction and Copywriting. After what I decide to move to Rome for new professionals challenges. I finally settled in Bologna in the early 2016 where I’m working as a freelance for both national and international brands.
As I’m convinced that diversity and cultural exchange is the key of creativity and success I never miss an occasion to travel, meeting people and discover new cultures. I’m always looking for connecting myself to more and more people from all other the globe who share the same interest and considerations.
